  SkillName: Abyssal Guillotine
  Description: "A focused, high-speed execution strike. The Maou vanishes into a burst\n
    of red mist and instantly reappears behind the highest-threat target, bringing\n
    his Odachi down in a catastrophic, concentrated vertical slash. Deals massive\n
    burst Magic Damage to a single target. This attack completely ignores enemy\n
    Armor and Shields, and instantly executes targets that are below a 20% health\n
    threshold."
